OL,3,CRetail NI warns businesses may face a
OL,4,Ccliff edge in the first half of 2025
OL,6,FRetail NI has warned that businesses
OL,7,Fmay face a cliff edge in the first
OL,8,Fhalf of 2025, as all National
OL,9,FInsurance, living wage and business
OL,10,Frates are set to increase.
OL,12,FAs shoppers hit the high street on
OL,13,FChristmas Eve for a last-minute dash,
OL,14,Fretailers said they're hoping to take
OL,15,Fin as much as possible to cushion
OL,16,Fagainst challenges in the new year.
OL,18,F"April does worry me," Glyn Roberts
OL,19,Ffrom Retail NI told UTV.
