OL,3,CRetail NI warns businesses may face a
OL,4,Ccliff edge in the first half of 2025
OL,6,F"With so many increases coming at the
OL,7,Fone time it really does worry me. I
OL,8,Fthink it will cause significant
OL,9,Fchallenges, not only for the retail
OL,10,Fsector, but for all our small
OL,11,Fbusinesses.
OL,13,F"It will disproportionately hit
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland the hardest, because
OL,15,Fwe have a higher density of small
OL,16,Fbusinesses that no other part of the
OL,17,FUK has."
OL,19,FIt comes as official figures show a
OL,20,Fless than impressive picture.
